HEADWORD: go-slow
<hw>go-slow</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A form of labor protest by workers
in which they deliberately slow down in order to cause problems for
their employers.</def> <mark>[British]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

